<a href="http://www.odi.org.uk/resources/download/5912.pdf" target="_self">http://www.odi.org.uk/resources/download/5912.pdf</a></p><p>8.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; United Nations, ‘The Common Agricultural Policy towards 2020: The role of the European Union in supporting the realization of the right to food’, 17 June 2011</p><p>
