<a href="http://eca.europa.eu/portal/pls/portal/docs/1/13768739.PDF" target="_self">http://eca.europa.eu/portal/pls/portal/docs/1/13768739.PDF</a></p><p>11.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; EC, DG Agriculture and Rural Development, ‘Financing the Common Agricultural Policy’, web page</p><p>
